Advanced Styling and JavaScript 🚀
This project demonstrates advanced techniques in CSS and JavaScript to build responsive and interactive web applications. It includes:

Responsive design with CSS media queries

An interactive quiz using JavaScript

Fetching and displaying live data from a public API

📁 Project Structure
bash
Copy
Edit
.
├── index.html       # Main HTML file
├── style.css        # Responsive CSS styling
└── script.js        # Quiz logic and API integration

🌐 1. Responsive Design with Media Queries
Uses CSS media queries to ensure the layout and typography adapt to different screen sizes including mobile, tablet, and desktop.

Key Features:

Fluid layout

Font scaling

Background color adaptation

🧠 2. JavaScript Interactive Quiz
A simple two-question multiple-choice quiz implemented with vanilla JavaScript.

Features:

Dynamic rendering of questions

Score tracking

Input validation

🛠 Technologies Used
HTML5

CSS3 (Media Queries)

JavaScript (ES6)

Fetch API

